tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE healthcare_records (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(100),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(255),
  treatment_plan VARCHAR(500),
  machine_learning_algorithm VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  patient_age INT,
  patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Treatments (
  treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
  treatment_description TEXT,
  treatment_cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
  treatment_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE MachineLearningModels (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR(50),
  model_description TEXT,
  model_accuracy DECIMAL(5, 2),
  model_framework VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    patient_age INT,
    patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
    patient_diagnosis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Treatments (
    treatment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
    treatment_type VARCHAR(50),
    treatment_date TIMESTAMP,
    treatment_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Diagnoses (
    diagnosis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
    diagnosis_date TIMESTAMP,
    diagnostic_algorithm VARCHAR(50),
    diagnosis_details TEXT
);
